Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:16.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:17.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] So, girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think about\Nthis new face of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Be honest--\NPretty hideous, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:23.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty sad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty ironic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:29.07,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish was to\Nruin Iona's career.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:31.95,Main,,0,0,0,,But the only thing\Nthat got ruined was my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:35.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It was my intention\Nto end her modeling career.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:38.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But it happened to me instead.\NFreaking insane, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:40.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[crazed giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:42.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NC'mon, it's funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:44.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[crazed giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] You should be laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:49.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[crazed giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:52.84,Main,,0,0,0,,--[AKIRA] Laugh, damn it!\N--[YUZUKI] Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] I used to be super-cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,but now look\Nat what I've become!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm not too\NAki-lucky anymore, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:00:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:00.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a freaking mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.23,0:01:03.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Back off, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] This is all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:07.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] I lost to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.49,0:01:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] And now I'm all alone\Nwith this jacked-up face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:15.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's fix that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.08,0:01:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] You and you and Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna carve all your faces\Nup so you look just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:23.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[POLICE OFFICER A]\NWhat are you kids doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:26.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[POLICE OFFICER A] Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:28.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay right there, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:32.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko! Let's book it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:33.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] She kept her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Uh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:49.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Then we're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] No, we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:53.49,Main,,0,0,0,,This is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:55.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira's right about\Nthe stuff she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Her wish getting\Ncorrupted is my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:00.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Look,\Nyou still don't have a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You should quit now\Nwhile you're ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:09.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:11.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:12.84,Main,,0,0,0,,If something bad happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.51,Main,,0,0,0,,think about what it\Nwould do to your grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.22,Main,,0,0,0,,The same thing goes\Nfor you, too, Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:18.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Think about how\Nyour parents would feel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,if something happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:21.97,Main,,0,0,0,,And Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:24.35,Main,,0,0,0,,He'd be heartbroken,\Nwouldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I can't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:30.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:33.19,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you saw what\Nlosing did to Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NI won't end up like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you don't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:38.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It's sweet of you\Nto worry, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:42.58,Main,,0,0,0,,No, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to keep pushing,\Njust a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I've come way too far\Nto give up on my dream now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:51.71,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'm this close\Nto making it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:53.55,Main,,0,0,0,,So--God, I hate this--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't be friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.43,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I'm\Ngoing to be an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.14,Main,,0,0,0,,If you keep\Nhanging around with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,our friendship could\Nbe used against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.60,Main,,0,0,0,,and I don't\Nwant you to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:04.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:06.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:09.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki! Please, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:15.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] It was really\Nfun being your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:16.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Our matching scrunchies?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I will treasure that forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:19.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Next time we meet,\NI'll be a new me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.66,Main,,0,0,0,,No more regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:26.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll finally be Kazuki's\Ngirlfriend for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Hey... Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:26.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Call home if\Nyou're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,And where in the world have\Nyou been all this time, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[slap lands]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:51.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine, so it's not\Nmy business or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:54.31,Main,,0,0,0,,But still, you shouldn't\Nworry Grandma like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:59.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she--\NIs she home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Go let her know\Nyou're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Oh, thank\Ngoodness you're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Cold cold, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Lucky for you\NI made some hot cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling you'd be cold
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,after walking\Noutside for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you asking me\Nquestions about where I've been?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Because, dear, I know\Nwhen you're ready to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.58,Main,,0,0,0,,...you'll let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Sound good to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:05.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:14.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Did the hot cider taste yummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Are you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:23.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish you were awake\Nand having a battle
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,'cause I like seeing\Nhow much fun you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.07,Main,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:33.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] There's one thing\Nthat I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Seeing you sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI yawning]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Morning, Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Whoa, you made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Yep, sure did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,And by some miracle, I didn't\Neven burn down the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:56.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, I made soup, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] For soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.85,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that you finally\Ncame out of your room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,after last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:02.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NGirls have days like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:06.36,Main,,0,0,0,,so the best thing to do is\Nsteer clear and leave 'em be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, say no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Good, now eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. And thanks for cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,The last time you\Nmade French toast,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.63,Main,,0,0,0,,it was a real\Ndisaster, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:27.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I used to rush things\Nway too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Lose my cool and mess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.76,Main,,0,0,0,,No more of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.68,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause I've learned\Nto calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Take my time and set my sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.56,Main,,0,0,0,,That way everything\Nworks out in the end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Seeing some friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:49.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't be gone for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.66,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm making\Ndinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what\Nwe should have?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.37,Main,,0,0,0,,We had French toast for\Nbreakfast, so for dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,--Curry udon!\N--Curry udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right, Kazuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you better\Nthan you know yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:09.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:10.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotta jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Cool, have a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hitoe. I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:30.40,Main,,0,0,0,,but I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:34.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't lose and\Nend up like you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I'm gonna make\Nmy wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:56.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[MALE SHOPKEEPER A] Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:12.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTOR B] Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you write that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:20.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTOR B] Not trying\Nto get on your case,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:24.42,Main,,0,0,0,,but isn't it kinda dangerous\Nto find opponents like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Yeah, I dunno,\Nyou're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTOR B] Look, personally,\NI don't have a problem with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.92,Main,,0,0,0,,but I could see where\Nother Selectors would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Even my LRIG thinks\Nit's kinda sketchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I can't wait for\Nopponents to come find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to get this\Nthing done already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.77,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.23,Main,,0,0,0,,After I beat you,\Nmy wish will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:48.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, pretty\Nconfident, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:49.52,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,--Open!\N--Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:05.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Something tells me\Ntoday's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:12.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nit is, but I feel different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it's\Nthe end of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Perhaps so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo! Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:25.27,Main,,0,0,0,,This girl is crazy serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] It's not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It never was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care\Nwhat people think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] The bond we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:39.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA] When I see you\Nstalking him all day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,it just makes me\Nfeel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] The love I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] That is super-duper\Nnaughty--You dirty girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:50.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Fissure of Condemnation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Direct Damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I'm not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I can change it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:05.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NNo matter what it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let this world\Ndeny my feelings anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.40,Main,,0,0,0,,...Kazuki will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 6B] Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Dude, you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:26.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're so good, Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:28.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 8A]\NGood? He's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 8A] Now it's my turn\Nand you're goin' down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 6B]\NNo way I'm losing to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, so can you\Ntake a look at my deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're gonna use Red?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.89,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause I think the\Ngem-themed SIGNI is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:43.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki thinks so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You know,\NI'm a little thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,If I get juice,\Ncan I bring it in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:55.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA]\NKazuki, will you come with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Hey, wait...\NWhat about--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,No, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA]\NSorry I had to trick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I just said the\Nwhole juice thing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,because I couldn't think of\Na better way to get you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.01,Main,,0,0,0,,...we could go out together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:30.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I do like you, Honoka,\Nbut just not in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Because there's\Nsomebody else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.78,Main,,0,0,0,,No, there's\Nnobody else, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA] Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,What about Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:45.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not because of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:46.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You two are\Nalways together,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,so you can't blame\Npeople for thinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:49.91,Main,,0,0,0,,We all know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:51.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You all know what?\NWhat are people thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:57.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Duh, that you and Yuzuki\Nare like, "doing stuff!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:59.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA] Everyone says you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:01.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is "everyone?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:04.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's so messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Who'd even say\Nthat kind of sicko crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.52,Main,,0,0,0,,How could you think\Nsuch a thing about Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,So who was it? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:15.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Or Senda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me some names now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go set 'em straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:21.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if the\Nrumors aren't true,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:24.07,Main,,0,0,0,,why are you so upset over\Nwhat people say about you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.78,Main,,0,0,0,,If I'm wrong about\Nyour weird relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,then prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:30.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, prove it how?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:31.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:35.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, since I\Nbared my soul to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:38.21,Main,,0,0,0,,the least you could\Ndo is give me a kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.00,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're single and\Nnot doing something weird
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:41.76,Main,,0,0,0,,with your sister,\Nwhat's the harm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.59,Main,,0,0,0,,This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.64,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Kazuki, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:51.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Something...\Nis definitely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon Cannon and with\Nits effect, banish Lotus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTOR B screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:01.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I don't feel like\NI have a fever or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,but I'm burning up inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:06.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this a sign\Nthat maybe my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:08.32,Main,,0,0,0,,It will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.83,Main,,0,0,0,,At last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] You are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:23.59,Main,,0,0,0,,If you do win this battle, your\Nfondest wish will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO]\NAre you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.56,Main,,0,0,0,,When I saw\Nwhat Hitoe became,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:35.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I was mad that you\Nkept me in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you had told\Nme what could happen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.61,Main,,0,0,0,,right from the\Nvery beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I would have wanted\Nto keep on fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care what it might take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:47.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll become an Eternal Girl\Nat any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, attack with Eagle! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:52.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:55.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I've gotta do this for my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:58.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel really bad about\Nwhat happened to Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:59.58,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Her wish was something\Nthat could come true
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.17,Main,,0,0,0,,without being a Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] But mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.18,Main,,0,0,0,,People will always frown on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I need power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I need a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Since you've\Nmade your decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,let us join together\Nfor one final attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:31.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, the oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,"I accept..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.71,Main,,0,0,0,,"...the laws of the Selector."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:41.13,Main,,0,0,0,,"I accept the laws\Nof the Selector."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:42.21,Main,,0,0,0,,And, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,"And upon this sacred oath,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.80,Main,,0,0,0,,a new Eternal Girl\Nshall be born!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO, YUZUKI]\NAdamasphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTOR B screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:16:59.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] It is the birth\Nof a new Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:12.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NWait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:14.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:21.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:33.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] It's your\Nday off from school, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:35.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you rather\Nbe playing your card game?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:37.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Mm, nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I always have\Na good time with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.98,Main,,0,0,0,,no matter what\Nwe do. And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.77,Main,,0,0,0,,...WIXOSS battles\Nmight be fun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,after seeing all\Nthe pain they cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:54.16,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't be friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:17:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:01.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Just trying to swallow a hiccup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.79,Main,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I have to stay away\Nfrom those cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:11.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[phone vibrating]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:12.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 8A] Dude, why did\Nyou take off like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Honoka's pretty ticked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:17.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She said you\Ntreated her like crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You gotta apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:21.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll help you\Nsmooth things over,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:22.69,Main,,0,0,0,,but get back here right--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are girls\Nsuch drama queens?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:29.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Yuzuki's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:32.19,Main,,0,0,0,,She's always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,And honest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:35.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if she's upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.87,Main,,0,0,0,,She tries to keep it to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA] Duh, that you and\NYuzuki are like, "doing stuff!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] No, that's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:57.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[tumbling noise]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO'S voice] Just got\Ndizzy for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, you better lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:09.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:15.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)]\NThank you, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:23.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you put something on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Like perfume?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You smell nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:32.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, they say if you\Nlike someone's natural smell,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:35.34,Main,,0,0,0,,that person is\Nthe love of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't come up\Nwith the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Just saying, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.27,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, what are\Nyou talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're trying\Nto make me laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:46.44,Main,,0,0,0,,this is just kinda awkward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:47.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you like your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.86,Main,,0,0,0,,the "love of your life"\Nis someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)]\NAnd if I was someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Other than my twin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We were born as\Ntwo halves of one whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.74,Main,,0,0,0,,so in order for\Nus to be complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,...maybe we just\Nneed to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:07.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:08.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)] With who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:09.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] You.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.13,Main,,0,0,0,,My friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Did someone say\Nsomething to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:17.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You can talk to me\Nabout anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.68,Main,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:20.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm yours if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)] Now and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:45.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[knocking]
